jwt.helpText:
- STEP 1: Go to www.jwt.io

- STEP 2: in header:
{

"alg": "HS256",
 "typ": "JWT",
"kid": "<<YOUR APP KEY>>"
}

- STEP 3: in payload:
{
"scope": "app"
}

- STEP 4: in signature, put the secret that matches the key you provided in the header
on the left part, youâ€™ll get your token (jwt)
